17:28.061 --> 17:31.441
<b>And all we have here are
merely royals of the lower world.</b>

17:31.441 --> 17:35.471
<b>Of course, you have to give a god
whatever he wants.</b>

17:35.471 --> 17:37.891
<b>He's right-<i>eh</i>, you idiots!</b>

17:37.891 --> 17:40.721
<b>That's not fair and it 
doesn't make any sense!</b>

17:40.721 --> 17:43.271
<b>A god doesn't need to make sense.</b>

17:43.771 --> 17:45.441
<b>Vivi-<i>chan</i>-<i>sama</i>...</b>

17:49.521 --> 17:51.091
<b><i>Otohime...</i></b>

17:51.091 --> 17:55.131
<b><i>The world that you dreamed
to live in side-by-side with humans is...</i></b>

17:55.131 --> 17:57.161
<b><i>The world under the sun is...</i></b>

17:58.711 --> 18:01.041
<b>Give me back Shirahoshi! She's my friend!</b>

18:08.501 --> 18:10.931
<b>Wait, Princess of Alabasta!</b>

18:10.931 --> 18:12.511
<b>King Neptune!</b>

18:12.771 --> 18:16.651
<b>Thank you! I won't forget your kindness!</b>

18:16.651 --> 18:20.681
<b>I'm afraid I must let it go now-<i>jamon</i>!</b>

18:20.681 --> 18:21.811
<b>What?!</b>

18:25.891 --> 18:29.941
<b>I'll kick their butts
and go back to the sea bottom-<i>jamon</i>!</b>

18:32.981 --> 18:35.571
<b>No! Don't hit him!</b>

18:35.831 --> 18:39.741
<b>If this is how life on the surface would be,
I can't bring my people anyway!</b>

18:39.741 --> 18:41.991
<b>No! This isn't how it'd be!</b>

18:42.451 --> 18:45.081
<b>King Neptune! They don't represent humans!</b>

18:48.761 --> 18:51.561
<b><i>I'm sorry, Otohime...</i></b>

18:53.341 --> 18:55.831
<b>Let's face them together!</b>

18:56.461 --> 19:04.431
<b>Then maybe we can make a difference
for the future of the children on this island,</b>

19:05.811 --> 19:08.101
<b>even just a small one!</b>

19:09.441 --> 19:14.961
<b><i>Even if we give them our 
love, humans won't change!</i></b>

19:14.961 --> 19:18.491
<b><i>I have to save Shirahoshi... Forgive me!</i></b>

19:18.491 --> 19:22.151
<b>Do you dare to defy me?
Kill him, Cipher Pol 0!</b>

19:22.151 --> 19:22.881
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

19:22.881 --> 19:24.121
<b>Get out of my way!</b>

19:24.121 --> 19:27.161
<b>Stop, Neptune the Great Night!
Don't jump the gun!</b>

19:29.251 --> 19:32.791
<b>Father-<i>sama</i>... no!
We should not hate anyone!</b>

19:43.681 --> 19:44.861
<b>Ugh...</b>

19:47.891 --> 19:50.981
<b>Who punched a Celestial Dragon?!</b>

19:50.981 --> 19:54.941
<b>I-I have nothing to do with this!
Okay, you fools?!</b>

19:59.491 --> 20:03.571
<b>I'm sorry...
As a fellow Celestial Dragon, I feel ashamed!</b>

20:04.831 --> 20:06.621
<b>Please forgive us!</b>

20:08.081 --> 20:10.001
<b>Is he a Celestial Dragon?!</b>

20:10.001 --> 20:12.831
<b>Let go of the Princess, you idiot!</b>

20:15.671 --> 20:20.591
<b>My apologies to everyone!
This fool brought panic to a place meant for socializing!</b>

20:22.801 --> 20:26.511
<b>I assume you don't remember me, Neptune...</b>

20:27.411 --> 20:33.271
<b>But I was indebted to the Ryugu Kingdom
and have been waiting for this day!</b>

20:33.651 --> 20:36.191
<b>The day that you all would come here...</b>

20:37.151 --> 20:38.861
<b>Don't tell me you're...</b>

20:41.821 --> 20:45.341
<b>I'm a silly Celestial Dragon...</b>

20:45.341 --> 20:48.741
<b>...who drifted down to the 
Ryugu Kingdom a decade ago...</b>

20:49.411 --> 20:52.871
<b>Hurry up and save my life, you fools!</b>

20:56.671 --> 20:59.591
<b>Don't do it, fools! Know your place!</b>

20:59.591 --> 21:02.471
<b>Who do you think I am?!</b>

21:02.471 --> 21:04.761
<b>--Kill him!
--Make him suffer!</b>

21:04.761 --> 21:06.261
<b>Show him no mercy!</b>

21:06.261 --> 21:07.471
<b>Don't do it!</b>

21:07.471 --> 21:09.141
<b>You stupid fish!</b>

21:27.161 --> 21:29.541
<b>Queen Otohime!!</b>

21:29.541 --> 21:31.721
<b>The Queen has been shot!</b>

21:42.511 --> 21:44.051
<b>Queen Otohime...</b>

21:44.511 --> 21:48.391
<b>Everybody, drop your gun!</b>

21:50.891 --> 21:52.851
<b>Children are watching!</b>

21:59.651 --> 22:01.261
<b>Otohime-<i>sama</i>...</b>

22:03.071 --> 22:04.601
<b>It's just a scratch.</b>

22:04.991 --> 22:06.491
<b>Why do you protect him?</b>

22:06.491 --> 22:10.071
<b>You don't know what he did to us in the past!</b>

22:10.071 --> 22:14.291
<b>I can feel your anguish - it's very painful.</b>

22:15.081 --> 22:16.751
<b>I know it's hard but...</b>

22:17.491 --> 22:23.461
<b>...you can't plant your anger and resentment
toward humans in children's mind!</b>

22:25.421 --> 22:28.641
<b>They need a chance to meet humans
and figure them out on their own.</b>

22:33.161 --> 22:40.751
<b>SAINT DONQUIXOTE MJOSGARD
A WORLD NOBLE (CELESTIAL DRAGON)</b>

22:33.721 --> 22:36.121
<b>I was admonished by the late Queen Otohime</b>

22:36.121 --> 22:38.291
<b>and became a decent human!</b>

22:38.291 --> 22:40.901
<b>I would do anything to help your people!</b>

22:41.481 --> 22:46.471
<b>King Neptune! It's my honor to see you again!</b>

22:46.471 --> 22:49.161
<b>Cipher Pol! Retreat from here!</b>

23:09.971 --> 23:13.311
<b><i>Kaido and Big Mom talk to each other about going after Luffy!
</i></b>

23:13.311 --> 23:15.831
<b>The two angry Emperors of 
the Sea are on the move!</b>

23:16.411 --> 23:20.171
<b><i>While the Navy raises the level of caution
to deal with the unprecedented situation,</i></b>

23:20.171 --> 23:25.071
<b><i>an even more unimaginable thing is about
to happen in Mariejois!</i></b>

23:25.071 --> 23:26.551
<b>On the next episode of One Piece!</b>

23:26.551 --> 23:30.331
<b>"An Explosive Situation! Two Emperors 
of the Sea Going After Luffy!"</b>

23:30.331 --> 23:32.701
<b>I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!</b>
